# NOTE: source/1-asm-6502/bank_NN_labeled.asm (code banks 0/1/2/15) ARE versioned.
# They are regenerated from mesen-labels.toml by `py -3 mesen-labels.py --asm` and
# MUST stay in sync with it — `py -3 mesen-labels.py --verify` exits 1 on drift
# (wire into CI / pre-commit). The old gitignored tool-output name *_named.asm is
# retired: the tool now writes the committed *_labeled.asm directly.

